{{Infobox Berry |name = Iapapa |image = [[File:Iapapa.png]] |caption = This Berry is very big and sour. The juiciness of the pulp accuentuates sourness. |growtime = 6m 20s |harvest = 18 berries |replant = 30% |points = 60 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 15 }} '''Iapapa''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 25, but no more than 80 points of sour and less than 5 points of all other flavours. The [[Aspear]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry.
